ior solution‚Äîfrom precise on-site\n        measurements and architectural drawings to immersive <strong>3D visualizations<\/strong>, allowing the client to\n        experience every detail before production began.\n      <\/p>\n\n      <p>\n        The grand main living room was designed around a large <strong>custom sectional sofa<\/strong>, perfectly\n        proportioned to the space. With <strong>double-height ceilings<\/strong>, we implemented\n        <strong>custom-sized drapery<\/strong> to complement the vertical scale, and due to the oversized floor plan, a\n        <strong>bespoke custom carpet<\/strong> was created to anchor the room. Elegant\n        <strong>wall paneling<\/strong> was added to enhance the soaring walls and create architectural depth.\n      <\/p>\n\n      <p>\n        In the dining room, we designed a <strong>137.7‚Äù custom sinterflex dining table<\/strong>, crafted in\n        <strong>two monumental pieces<\/strong> to achieve both scale and functionality. The sinterflex slabs were\n        <strong>specially sourced from Italy<\/strong>, bringing refined European craftsmanship into the heart of the\n        home. This bespoke table comfortably seats 16 guests and serves as a striking centerpiece for large gatherings.\n        Decorative wall finishes were applied to further enrich the dining area‚Äôs atmosphere.\n      <\/p>\n\n      <p>\n        One of the most distinctive aspects of this project was incorporating several of the client‚Äôs\n        <strong>traditional heirloom pieces<\/strong> into the overall design, creating a sophisticated blend of personal\n        heritage and modern luxury.\n      <\/p>\n\n      <p>\n        <strong>Sharma‚Äôs Residence<\/strong> showcases Saloni Furniture US‚Äôs signature approach: precise planning, fully\n        customized solutions, and seamless execution. From the first sketches to the final 3D renderings, our team\n        collaborated closely with the client to craft a home that balances grandeur with intimacy.\n      <\/p>\n\n      <p><strong class=\"team\">Project Team:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n      <ul>\n        <li><strong>Architect:<\/strong> Emre Ozkaya<\/li>\n        <li><strong>Lead Designer:<\/strong> Sirin Ozkaya<\/li>\n        <li><strong>Project Manager:<\/strong> Harun Uzulmez<\/li>\n        <li><strong>3D Visualization Artist:<\/strong> Kadir Aydinli<\/li>\n      <\/ul>\n\n      <p>\n        Every detail of <strong>Sharma‚Äôs Residence<\/strong> was meticulously designed to create a one-of-a-kind living\n        experience, proving that true luxury lies in personalization.\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n  .pdf-buttons-section {\n    padding: 60px 20px;\n  }\n\n  .content-container {\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  .main-title {\n    font-size: 36px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-align: left;\n    margin-bottom: 30px;\n    color: #333;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n  }\n\n  .project-info {\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\n  }\n\n  .subtitle {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    color: #333;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n    font-weight: 500;\n  }\n\n  .address {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #666;\n    margin-bottom: 0;\n  }\n\n  .description {\n    margin-bottom: 50px;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n  }\n\n  .description p {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #333;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    text-align: justify;\n  }\n\n  .description p .team {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    color: #333;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n\n  .description ul {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #333;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    text-align: justify;\n  }\n\n  .description li {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #333;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    text-align: justify;\n  }\n\n  .pdf-buttons-container {\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 30px;\n    justify-content: center;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n  }\n\n  .pdf-download-btn {\n    background-color: #a4b93a;\n    color: #33